{What is the best way to deal with White's initiative?} 15... Be6 $1 {Very
strong move! Black closes the e-file which is White's main positional asset
here.} 16. dxe6 f6 17. Re3 c6 $1 {We are following the main line of this
variation in which according to my analyses Black has an advantage. Let's
continue a little bit more.} 18. Rh3 {After exchanging the rooks, White's
queen could invade Black's camp. How to prevent it?} Rxh3 19. gxh3 g6 $1 {This
is the last precise move. White has run out of constructive ideas has a
difficult position.} *

