trapped.} 13. Ng3 Qd7 {Black is connecting his rooks.} 14. Bd2 Bb6 $1 {After
closing the b-file, Black is ready to follow with Rad8. His position is
already slightly preferable thanks to the strong center and the better
coordinated pieces.} *

